$225 INCLUDES CONUS SHIPPING
This is not just for the base game, but for my entire collection. Not a lifelong complete set or anything, but lots of cool stuff in here to start you off on Dust Tactics. Using the FF ruleset, not the new one, but all of this can be adapted to the new 2.0 rules simply by adding the new card decks and dice (optional).
Includes:
Dust Tactics: Revised Core Set
Dust Tactics: Terrain Tile Set x2. Corners slightly bumped due to how FF packages them, but got a replacement set from MM and now have two.
Dust Tactics: Unit Card Upgrade Pack - Contains the updated (from original to FF) point values for ALL units available at the time. Allows proxying of unowned units with other models.
Extra original dice - Ordered these directly from the game designer. An extra set of 12 (or 15) dice to make combat resolution easier (roll all you need at one time, etc.)
Custom Made unit cards - Scanned the unit cards and had printed professionally into a deck of smaller standard cards. Takes up less space on the table. All cards from the upgrade pack as well as all units included.
Custom Made initiative cards - Small deck size of cards to use for playing the game solitaire. Shuffle the cards for each unit in play and then draw to see which activates next.
